Name: script debug mode

Synonyms: script debug mode,script debugging mode,script debugger mode

Type: glossary

Description:
Mode of the LiveCode <development environment> in which the Script Debug window is open. When in script debug mode, <execute|executing> the <breakpoint> <command> halts the current <handler>.

